title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX-07

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR PX-07

Boss Air 12 Volt Air Compressor PX-07 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Suitable for industrial and automotive use. Up to 30L tanks. Best used with an air tank.

Specs:

  • 12volt compressor
  • 3/4 hp engine
  • 100% duty cycle
  • 170ltr free flow rate (approx 3.5cfm)
  • Recommended working pressure 0-150psi maximum pressure 200psi – 31.5 amp maximum draw
  • Fan cooled engine and cylinder head
  • Oil free design
  • 3/8npt ported head
  • Rebuildable design
  • Crank case fed – external washable air filter
  • Cast aluminum legs
  • Special piston valve design for maximum performance

PLEASE NOTE: MUST USE CHECK VALVE TO PREVENT BACK FLOW+ 40 AMP FUSE – NEVER OIL THIS COMPRESSOR

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
